name: Elijah Brewer
profile_summary: This 31-year-old man stands at 6'2" and works in the Technology industry as a Software Developer. He studied at Stanford University and is of Black African descent. His relationship preference is monogamy for a long-term intention. He identifies his sexuality as straight and is presently childless yet hopes to have children in the future. His pet preference includes dogs. Leo is his zodiac sign. He maintains an active lifestyle, occasionally enjoys a drink, but does not smoke, use marijuana, or other drugs.
